OL,5,G2340 Not Going Out
OL,6,     FFront Window: Confined to a
OL,7,     Fwheelchair after knee surgery, Lee
OL,8,     Fhas too much time on his hands and
OL,9,     Fuses it to watch the world go by
OL,10,     Fthrough a pair of high-powered
OL,11,     Fbinoculars.
OL,12,G0020 Not Going Out
OL,13,     FJury: Lee does jury service and
OL,14,     Fjoins eleven other jurors to
OL,15,     Fdebate a case. It's a simple
OL,16,     Fenough task... that is, until Lee
OL,17,     Fdecides to put the other jurors on
OL,18,     Ftrial.
